  "title": "Male sterility",
  "abstract": "In an F2 population from the cross Annigeri X PM-L550, two naturally occurring male-sterile plants were found. The F1 from crosses of these plants with G130 had normal meiosis and were fully fertile and the F2 indicated that male sterility was partial, without clear-cut segregation.",
